title: East Palo Alto rebounds as crime plummets, economy thrives
text:
Photo: Lea Suzuki, The Chronicle Dempsey Mitchell, a driver with the East Palo Alto Senior Center, greets Police Chief Albert Pardini (center) and Cmdr. Jerry Alcaraz. Palo Alto police have made community outreach a major priority. Dempsey Mitchell, a driver with the East Palo Alto Senior Center,...
East Palo Alto Police Chief Albert Pardini strolled the tree-lined streets of his city with a grin and a wave for everyone he passed. They waved and smiled back.
